<body>
  <h1>Entity Examples</h1>
  <p>Non-breaking space:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;between words.</p>
  <p>Symbols: &copy; 2025 Example Corp. (same as &#169;)</p>
  <p>Literal ampersand: Tom &amp; Jerry</p>

  <h1>SVG Example</h1>
  <p>Below is a simple inline SVG rectangle with a circle inside:</p>
  <svg width="200" height="100">
    <rect width="200" height="100" fill="#eef" stroke="black" />
    <circle cx="100" cy="50" r="30" fill="red" />
    <text x="100" y="55" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" fill="black">SVG</text>
  </svg>

  <h1>MathML Example</h1>
  <p>Hereâ€™s an inline quadratic formula using MathML:</p>
  <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
    <mi>x</mi>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mfrac>
      <mrow>
        <mo>&#x2212;</mo> <!-- minus sign -->
        <mi>b</mi>
        <mo>&#x00B1;</mo> <!-- plus/minus -->
        <msqrt>
          <msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>
          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>
          <mn>4</mn><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi>
        </msqrt>
      </mrow>
      <mrow>
        <mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi>
      </mrow>
    </mfrac>
  </math>
</body>
